        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 11 at 5:27PM CDT until August 11 at 6:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>SVRAMA

The National Weather Service in Amarillo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Central Carson County in the Panhandle of Texas...

* Until 630 PM CDT.

* At 527 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Panhandle,
moving northeast at 5 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
Hail damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Panhandle.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
